#: ../../accelerometer.rst:2
msgid "Accelerometer"
msgstr "Akcelerometer"

#: ../../accelerometer.rst:6
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This object gives you access to the on-board accelerometer. The "
"accelerometer also provides convenience functions for detecting gestures."
" The recognised gestures are: ``up``, ``down``, ``left``, ``right``, "
"``face up``, ``face down``, ``freefall``, ``3g``, ``6g``, ``8g``, "
"``shake``."
msgstr ""
"Tento objekt vám umožňuje prístup k akcelerometru, ktorý je na doske "
"micro:bit-u. Akcelerometer tiež poskytuje pohodlné funkcie na detekciu "
"pohybových gest. Rozpoznané gestá sú: ``up``, ``down``, ``left``, "
"``right``, ``face up``, ``face down``, ``freefall``, ``3g``, ``6g``, "
"``8g``, ``shake``."

